Ralph E. Gomory - Wikipedia





















 






Ralph E. Gomory

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search



Ralph Gomory


Born
(1929-05-07) 7 May 1929 (age 88)[1]
Brooklyn Heights, New York


Nationality
American


Fields
Mathematics


Institutions
Thomas J. Watson Research Center


Alma mater
Williams College (B.A., 1950)
Princeton University (Ph.D., 1954)


Thesis
Critical Points at Infinity and Forced Oscillation (1954)


